object.customQuery:
WITH current_batch AS (
    SELECT 
        bls.batch_id,
        bls.source_start_cutoff_datetime,
        bls.source_end_cutoff_datetime
    FROM metal.batch_load_summary bls
    WHERE bls.source_system_code = 'ADM'
      AND bls.batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      AND bls.batch_id = (
          SELECT MAX(batch_id)
          FROM metal.batch_load_summary
          WHERE source_system_code = 'ADM'
            AND batch_status = 'Inprogress'
      )
)
SELECT DISTINCT 
metal_acp.source_name, 
metal_acp.load_type, 
metal_acp.agency_nup, 
metal_acp.bs_appoint_dt, 
metal_acp.bs_cancel_dt, 
metal_acp.ca_appoint_dt, 
metal_acp.ca_cancel_dt, 
metal_acp.create_user_nup, 
metal_acp.created, 
metal_acp.id, 
metal_acp.mk_appoint_dt, 
metal_acp.mk_cancel_dt, 
metal_acp.modified, modify_user_nup, 
metal_acp.state,
current_batch.batch_id
FROM metal.adm_commission_plans metal_acp
CROSS JOIN current_batch
ORDER BY 
metal_acp.id,
metal_acp.created,
metal_acp.modified

object.customQuery:
SELECT 
	commission_plans_row_id, 
	commission_plans_batch_id, 
	agency_id,
	commission_plan_id,
	commission_plans_md5checksum, 
	commission_plans_datetime_modified, 
	commission_plans_row_effective_end_datetime
FROM bronze.adm_commission_plans
WHERE commission_plans_row_effective_end_datetime = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
